305
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:00,870
This?

306
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:03,150
That's called a precise dig.

307
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,470
It's a real skill.

308
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,360
When the shovel goes down,

309
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,510
