310
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:11,150
That's the halfway lucky number.

311
00:14:11,742 --> 00:14:12,955
Can it really be that accurate?

312
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:15,440
Of course. You just haven't seen enough.

313
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:18,030
The stone slab!

314
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:20,150
I found one too!

315
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:23,390
Hey, Chen.

316
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,480
That's not cool of you.

317
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:27,360
After all these years,

318
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:29,600
