319
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:30,910
I already taught you long ago.

320
00:14:32,750 --> 00:14:33,590
You did?

321
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,440
Cut the chatter.

322
00:14:35,670 --> 00:14:36,670
Just watch carefully.

323
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,360
So, what's next?

324
00:14:40,150 --> 00:14:41,440
