325
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,390
Pair up.

326
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,390
You all saw what I just did.

327
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,120
First, straight down.

328
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,480
Second, tilt back 45 degrees.

329
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:50,510
