333
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,870
Everyone, got it?

334
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:58,800
Got it.

335
00:15:00,550 --> 00:15:02,390
Right. Grab a shovel and come with me.

336
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:03,660
Come on, hurry up.

337
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:04,960
All of you, grab a shovel.

338
00:15:05,150 --> 00:15:06,000
Take that shovel.

339
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,030
Two people per spot.

340
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:08,270
Don't move around.

341
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,000
Follow the instructions.

342
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:10,870
Come here.

343
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:14,150
Come on, move forward.

344
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:19,320
