378
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:29,840
One.

379
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:31,630
Two.

380
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,320
Three.

381
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,200
One.

382
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,230
Two.

383
00:16:40,360 --> 00:16:41,200
